<br>
Xanthe's Earring of Nature: <br>
AC 5, STR 8, STA 8, WIS 10, <br>
HP 55, MANA 55, FIRE 7, COLD 7, MAGIC 7, <br>
Effect: Circle of the Combines; <br>
Recommended Level 51, DRU/ALL, NO DROP, LORE<br>
<br>
BUT!  You can turn this in to receive the Earring of the Solstice!<br>
<br>
Earring of the Solstice: <br>
AC 5, STA 5, WIS 8, INT 8, <br>
HP 55, MANA 55, FIRE 5, COLD 5, MAGIC 5, <br>
Effect: Flowing Thought I, <br>
Recommended Level 51, ALL/ALL, NO DROP, LORE<br>
<br>
All it takes is money!  And if you are the least bit discerning about your fashion tastes, what is a little cash between raid days?<br>
<br>
Here's the Shopping List for the bazaar!<br>
<br>
Demi-Sec Champagne           (150)<br>
Mistletoe Cutting Sickle         (3000)<br>
Golden Idol of Tunare            (2500)<br>
Blessed Fishing Rod               (1500)<br>
Star Ruby Encrusted Stein     (500)<br>
Ceremonial Solstice Robe        (1250)<br>
Lotus Pie                             (50)<br>
Misty Thicket Picnic               (75)<br>
Lucky Cabbage                     (25)<br>
<br>
So, the fact remains, you can either spend 30,000 platinum to learn how to make all of these items yourself, OR you can pay approximately 9,050 platinum and have someone else slave over that for you!  They get to make a profit, you get to have a Flowing Thought Earring and EVERYONE is the better for it!<br>
<br>
Now, I know it's scary... but once you get all nine items, go over to the forge and place all nine in and combine them.  That's right!  It's a no fail combine in a forge.  You'll receive the druid earring and a NO DROP Druid scroll... just junk it... what do you need it for anyway?  Then go find Rebecca Cabbage Leaf in Fungus Grove and give her the druid earring.<br>
<br>
It's that easy, folks!  High fashion for low cash.  And the nice thing is, the Flowing Thought works REGARDLESS of LEVEL!<br>
<br>
When it's this easy, it would be foolish not to have this earring... and I'm totally serious about that.  Unfortunately, you must have Luclin for this quest. <p>Yunin D'Vestra - Fashion Queen of Bristlebane</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub39.ezboard.com/uyunin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yunin</A> at: 10/7/02 1:12:51 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://p079.ezboard.com/fsonsofkings26528frm11.showPrevMessage?topicID=11.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://p079.ezboard.com/fsonsofkings26528frm11.showNextMessage?topicID=11.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://p079.ezboard.com/fsonsofkings26528frm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://p079.ezboard.com/fsonsofkings26528frm11.emailToFriend?topicID=11.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://p079.ezboard.com/fsonsofkings26528frm11.threadControl?topicID=11.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://p079.ezboard.com/fsonsofkings26528frm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://p079.ezboard.com/fsonsofkings26528frm11.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of re